Developer Terms of Use
des: Listen to the latest sermons from West End Community Church. You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." Just say "Alexa, stop" when you're done for the day. When listening to podcasts you can say "Alexa, shuffle" to shuffle the playing order, or "Alexa, loop" to loop the current episode. You can also ask for previous and next episodes by saying "Alexa, previous" and "Alexa, next". You can also visit us online at west end c c dot org. Thank you for listening!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
